    // If current_post_sum is not 0 here, it means the last segment didn't sum up to target_post_duration,
    // which implies an issue, but the previous check `current_post_sum > target_post_duration`
    // and `total_duration % k != 0` should cover this.
    // The main check is `posts_formed == k`.
    if (posts_formed == k) {
