        // $median(C_1) = a_{(n-1)/2}$.
        // $median(C_2) = a_{n + (n-1)/2}$.
        // The difference is $a_{n + (n-1)/2} - a_{(n-1)/2}$.
        // This is not $a_n - a_{n-1}$ for $n > 1$.
