        // The problem is that the students are not necessarily contiguous in the sorted array.
        //
        // The solution is indeed $a_n - a_{n-1}$.
        // This is a known result for similar problems.
        // The minimum difference between medians of two partitions of an array of $2n$ elements into two odd-sized sets
